<i>noun</i>: 주입 [주ː입], 억수 [억쑤] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>주입 [주ː입]</dt><br>
<dd>1. injection</dd><br>
<dd>액체나 기체가 흘러 들어가도록 부어 넣음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of injecting a liquid or gas so it can flow into something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. pouring; cramming</dd><br>
<dd>교육에서, 주로 기억과 암기를 통해 학습자에게 지식을 넣어 줌.</dd><br>
<dd>In education, the act of instilling knowledge into the learner mainly through memory work and rote memory.</dd><br>
<dt>억수 [억쑤]</dt><br>
<dd>1. heavy rain; pouring rain</dd><br>
<dd>물이 쏟아지듯이 세차게 많이 내리는 비.</dd><br>
<dd>Torrential rain like the pouring of water.</dd><br>
<dd>2. torrents; flood; pouring</dd><br>
<dd>정도가 아주 심함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being very extraordinary in quantity, extent, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>